description:
Getting to Know Two Pioneering Adventist Ministers [History]

This week in Adventist history, we learn about two pioneering Adventist ministers who chose to serve the Lord in order to bring freedom, healing, and hope in Jesus to the early believers.

Watch the video to learn more about these two ministers who devoted their lives to sharing the gospel and leading people to Jesus.

Discover more exciting people and stories at https://encyclopedia.adventist.org/
Learn more about the Adventist Church and what we believe at https://www.adventist.org/
